item.description: IWD 328 observe its district Rally with much enthusiasm & zeal on 13 October, 2012 at Dhaka. This year the theme was ‘Be A Friend’. Mr Aly Zaker, one of our famous drama personalities was the Chief Guest. Dist. Chairman Suraiya Alam preside the rally. IWC of Dhaka, Dhaka South & Greater Dhaka jointly hosted the programme. Different cultural activities, dress as you like gave much entertainment to a huge audience.

item.description: First District Committee Meeting for the year 2012-13 was held on the September 8, 2012 at RAOWA Club from 10 a.m. to 1 p.m. Voting delegates from different clubs were present. District Chairman Suraiya Alam conducted the meeting in the presence of National Representative Naz Afreen Rahman. Tahera Muzaffar & Akhter Jahan was elected as National Representative & Deputy National Representative for the year 2013-14.

item.description: A professional Work-shop was held on June 23, 2012 at RAOWA Club from 10 a.m. to 2 p.m. The duties of all the District and Club level posts were explained by the District Digniteries on this programme. A workshop manual was distributed to all the Club Presidents as their guideline.The programe was started by Dist. Chairman Akhter Jahan, 2011-12 and then handed over to Suraiya Alam, Dist. Chairman 2012-13.

item.description: The District Assembly of ‘Vision & Action’ was held on Emmanuels Hotel, Dhaka 0n 22 June, 2012. Prof. Dr. M.R. Khan was the chief guest of the programe. District Chairman Presided over the meeting. Prominent mountain rider Wasfia & Nishat was recoznized by dist. 328. A huge number of members presence make the occasion colorful. The programe was finished by the award giving ceremony.
